<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        
        <title>Play Time</title>
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-+0n0xVW2eSR5OomGNYDnhzAbDsOXxcvSN1TPprVMTNDbiYZCxYbOOl7+AMvyTG2x" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-gtEjrD/SeCtmISkJkNUaaKMoLD0//ElJ19smozuHV6z3Iehds+3Ulb9Bn9Plx0x4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <style>
            .game-logo {
                width: 15%;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
            .game-logo img {
                width: 100%;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        
        <div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
            <div class="game-logo"><img class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="/assets/icons/game-logo.png" alt="logo"></div>
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Guess Pani Sollu</h1>
            <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
                <p class="lead mb-4">To start the game enter your team name in the below text box. Make sure your team name is therific. Most importantly I encourage all team mates to give their best fun. This is purely to enjoy. Games apart, just for fun.</p>
                <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
                    <form action="/play-time/" autocomplete="off" method="POST">
                        <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" type="text" name="playerName" placeholder="Enter Player Name" id="playerName">
                            <label for="floatingInput">Team Name</label>
                          </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 gap-3">Arambikalangalaa</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </body>
</html>